original_title: ONE Friday Fights 12: Petsukumvit vs. Kongthoranee
overview: ONE Friday Fights 12 (also known as ONE Lumpinee 12) was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on April 7, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand. A flyweight muay thai bout between Phetsukumvit Boybangna and Kongthoranee Sor.Sommai served as the event headliner.
title: ONE Friday Fights 12: Petsukumvit vs. Kongthoranee
